verbose_text: To complement these late Env structures and achieve a longitudinal comparison, we also obtained cryo-EM reconstructions of an early Env, PC64M4C054, expressed as a SOSIP.664 trimer (early SOSIP) in complex with both an antibody isolated from month 13, PCT64-13C (early Fab), and the late Fab at 5.1 A and 5.5 A resolution, respectively (XREF_FIG D, 1E, and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
